Interface CountingListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Listener, Registrable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCountingListener

    public interface CountingListener
extends Listener
    A listener capable of counting events. The events are identified by instances of implementations of CountingListener.Key interface.

    1.0
    Author:
